i - 書懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Qu%C3%BD-Th%C3%ADch/author-_a5NZkjlUmxBDVuBs6LQJg">Phạm Quý Thích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Tr%C3%B9ng-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-b%E1%BA%A5t-v%C5%A9/poem-AO3_tKxAUEogB2RY296FCw">Trùng dương bất vũ - 重陽不雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Linh/T%E1%BB%ADu-%C4%91%E1%BB%A9c-t%E1%BB%A5ng/poem-J13HP-vW93XWQ7-28U2Z0A">Tửu đức tụng - 酒德頌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Linh/author-hkIbirWYM3zvfGsJ_u2tHQ">Lưu Linh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Qu%C3%BD-Tuy%C3%AAn/Xu%C3%A2n-s%E1%BA%A7u-thi-hi%E1%BB%87u-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Xuy%C3%AAn-T%E1%BB%AD/poem-b0lVaHG5wN40Hu-ickJ1_g">Xuân sầu thi hiệu Ngọc Xuyên Tử - 春愁詩效玉川子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Qu%C3%BD-Tuy%C3%AAn/author-HlAsEr3qGyMOUeGTRRdhhQ">Tiết Quý Tuyên</a>)<br></div>	</div>
